	To create a custom About page 
	  1) create a new About Page (set page Template to page.about) 
	  2) Add your new page to the main navigation
	  3) Go to 'Customize Theme'
	  	3a) click on 'About Us' in main nav on the preview page
	  	3b) Here you can edit your about text and image in "About Page Text Area" section
	  	3c) You can edit your logo list by clicking the "Logo list" section
